OL,3,CWidow donates 10 treatment chairs to
OL,4,CGuernsey's cancer unit
OL,6,FA widow from Guernsey has donated 10
OL,7,Fnew treatment chairs to the Cancer
OL,8,FUnit at the Princess Elizabeth
OL,9,FHospital.
OL,11,FAnne Hutchings lost her husband
OL,12,FMichael to the disease and donated the
OL,13,Ffurniture in recognition of the care
OL,14,Fhe received whilst undergoing
OL,15,Ftreatment.
OL,17,FThe new chairs are remote control
OL,18,Foperated and can assist people getting
OL,19,Fup, they also have power ports so
OL,20,Fpatients can charge their phones and
OL,21,Flaptops.
