OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F386A1722625810
OL,3,CWidow donates 10 treatment chairs to
OL,4,CGuernsey's cancer unit
OL,6,FShe adds: "I think it will make a
OL,7,Fgreat difference, I am thrilled, I am
OL,8,Fover the moon. Some people might think
OL,9,Fwell a chair is a chair but these
OL,10,Fchairs are rather special."
OL,12,FLead cancer nurse Lucy Coggon
OL,13,Fexplains: "The sessions for treatment
OL,14,Fcan be anywhere from an hour up to
OL,15,Feight hours so it can be a really long
OL,16,Fday and it is really important that
OL,17,Fpeople feel comfortable whilst they
OL,18,Fare here.
