OL,3,CWidow donates 10 treatment chairs to
OL,4,CGuernsey's cancer unit
OL,6,F"The chairs also have a USB port so
OL,7,Fpeople can send messages to friends
OL,8,Fand family whilst undergoing
OL,9,Ftreatment, it is important that people
OL,10,Fhave their gadgets fully charged up
OL,11,Fwhilst they are here so that is
OL,12,Flovely."
OL,14,FAnne explains how her childhood played
OL,15,Fa role in her donation.
