OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F386A1722625810
OL,3,CWidow donates 10 treatment chairs to
OL,4,CGuernsey's cancer unit
OL,6,FShe says: "I grew up with generous
OL,7,Fparents, parents who gave, parents who
OL,8,Fdid not expect to be given things all
OL,9,Fthe time so I just feel it is part of
OL,10,Fme to give and my husband was like
OL,11,Fthat too.
OL,13,F"Caring to me is giving love and
OL,14,Fappreciation to other people, I had
OL,15,Fthat from my husband and he had that
OL,16,Ffrom the nurses here, they were warm,
OL,17,Fwelcoming and that is one of the many,
OL,18,Fmany reasons."
