OL,4,CGuernsey's cancer unit
OL,6,FGuernsey's Health and Social Care team
OL,7,Fadd: "The staff and patients in
OL,8,FBulstrode Oncology Unit are grateful
OL,9,Fto Anne for her generosity in funding
OL,10,Fnew furniture for the department.
OL,12,F"All the new treatment chairs are
OL,13,Fremote control operated and rise and
OL,14,Frecline which can assist people to get
OL,15,Fup when they are attached to a drip.
OL,16,FThey also have a footrest for comfort."
